== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavukiye kandi akurira i Padua, mu [[Ubutaliyani|Butaliyani]] . Kuva mu 1994, yabereye i Londres.  Afite impamyabumenyi y'ikirenga ya PhD muri kaminuza ya Westminster. <ref>https://www.westminster.ac.uk/about-us/our-people/directory/zoppelletto-cecilia-0</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Nkubushakashatsi bwe, yakoze Decolonisation akoresheje 'Amajyambere ya Filime': Kubaka no kongera kubaka Umwuka wa Zairian kuri Film. Binyuze mu bushakashatsi, akora ubushakashatsi ku bubiko bwa Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo ndetse n’ishusho ya firime y’igihugu nyuma y’ubwigenge. <ref name="africanfilmny">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://africanfilmny.org/directors/cecilia-zoppelletto/ "Cecilia Zoppelletto"]. African Filmny<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">30 October</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref> <ref>http://georgiatoday.ge/news/5125/INTERVIEW%3A-Cecilia-Zoppelletto,-Director,-Featured-in-GIFT-2016-</ref>

Yakoze nka producer wamakuru muri societe yigihugu yo mubutaliyani RAI. Hagati aho, yakoraga nka televiziyo akaba n'umwanditsi kuri neti yo mu Butaliyani 'Antenna Tre Nordest'. Muri 2015, yakoze documentaire ''La Belle Kuri Sinema'' . Iyi filime yamenyekanye cyane kandi yerekanwa muri [[Amerika]], Ububiligi, [[Ubwongereza]] na Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo. <ref>http://www.congoinharlem.org/belle</ref> Noneho muri 2017, yakoze firime ngufi ''Falling''. <ref name="africanfilmny">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://africanfilmny.org/directors/cecilia-zoppelletto/ "Cecilia Zoppelletto"]. African Filmny<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">30 October</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref>

